{"title":"ลองใช้งาน Recorder ใน Google Chrome 97 (Dev channel)","link":"https://www.somkiat.cc/recorder-in-google-chrome-97/","date":1636185573000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div id=\"page\"><article><div id=\"content_box\"><header></header><div><figure><img src=\"https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2564-11-06-at-14.41.43-1024x594.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2564-11-06-at-14.41.43-1024x594.png 1024w, https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2564-11-06-at-14.41.43-300x174.png 300w, https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2564-11-06-at-14.41.43-768x446.png 768w, https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2564-11-06-at-14.41.43-1536x891.png 1536w, https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2564-11-06-at-14.41.43.png 1830w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"></figure><p>มาลองดูความสามารถใหม่ใน <strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://developer.chrome.com/docs/devtools/recorder/\" target=\"_blank\">Google Chrome 97 (Dev channel) ที่ชื่อว่า Recorder</a></strong><br>สามารถทำการ record การใช้งาน web นั้น ๆ ไว้<br>จากนั้นทำการ replay ได้<br>รวมทั้งสามารถกำหนดความเร็วของระบบ network ที่ใช้งานอีกด้วย<br>เพื่อวัดผลการทำงานว่าเป็นอย่างไร</p><p><strong>สามารถเข้าไปเปิดใช้งานที่ DevTools -&gt; More Tools ดังรูป</strong></p><figure><img src=\"https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2564-11-06-at-14.44.54.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"501\" height=\"344\" srcset=\"https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2564-11-06-at-14.44.54.png 798w, https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2564-11-06-at-14.44.54-300x206.png 300w, https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2564-11-06-at-14.44.54-768x527.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 501px) 100vw, 501px\"></figure><p><strong>จากนั้นก็เริ่มใช้งานด้วยการสั่ง record ดังนี้</strong></p><figure><img src=\"https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2564-11-06-at-14.53.46-1024x591.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"288\" srcset=\"https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2564-11-06-at-14.53.46-1024x591.png 1024w, https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2564-11-06-at-14.53.46-300x173.png 300w, https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2564-11-06-at-14.53.46-768x443.png 768w, https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2564-11-06-at-14.53.46-1536x887.png 1536w, https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2564-11-06-at-14.53.46.png 1774w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"></figure><p><strong>ทำการ record ได้ดังนี้</strong></p><figure><img src=\"https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2564-11-06-at-14.55.16-1024x416.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2564-11-06-at-14.55.16-1024x416.png 1024w, https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2564-11-06-at-14.55.16-300x122.png 300w, https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2564-11-06-at-14.55.16-768x312.png 768w, https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2564-11-06-at-14.55.16-1536x624.png 1536w, https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2564-11-06-at-14.55.16-2048x832.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"></figure><p><strong>ทำการเลือกความเร็วของ network ได้</strong></p><figure><img src=\"https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2564-11-06-at-14.55.42.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"212\" height=\"226\" srcset=\"https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2564-11-06-at-14.55.42.png 476w, https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2564-11-06-at-14.55.42-281x300.png 281w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 212px) 100vw, 212px\"></figure><p><strong>อีกทั้งสามารถทำการ replay และ วัดเรื่องของ web performance ได้ดังนี้</strong></p><figure><img src=\"https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2564-11-06-at-14.56.09-1024x458.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2564-11-06-at-14.56.09-1024x458.png 1024w, https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2564-11-06-at-14.56.09-300x134.png 300w, https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2564-11-06-at-14.56.09-768x344.png 768w, https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2564-11-06-at-14.56.09-1536x688.png 1536w, https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2564-11-06-at-14.56.09-2048x917.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"></figure><p><strong>ยังไม่พอ ยังสามารถเพิ่ม assertion หรือ การตรวจสอบผลจาก action ต่าง ๆ ได้อีก</strong></p><figure><img src=\"https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2564-11-06-at-15.03.30.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"376\" height=\"324\" srcset=\"https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2564-11-06-at-15.03.30.png 682w, https://www.somkiat.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2564-11-06-at-15.03.30-300x259.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 376px) 100vw, 376px\"></figure><p>ลอง <strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.google.com/intl/en_uk/chrome/dev/\" target=\"_blank\">Download</a></strong> มาลองใช้งานกันดู<br>น่าจะมทีประโยชน์เยอะมาก ๆ สำหรับ web development</p></div><div><p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e5cb9aad7bf4f0e43462bd51d6ff7021?s=90&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g\" srcset=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e5cb9aad7bf4f0e43462bd51d6ff7021?s=180&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g 2x\" height=\"90\" width=\"90\"></p><h4>Article by <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/somkiatspns\">Somkiat Puisungnoen</a></h4><p>To be Craftmanship</p></div></div></article></div></div>","author":"somkiat","siteTitle":"cc :: somkiat","siteHash":"3a23a5a4389e1e40c6fbb16520